  "intro": "<h2 class=\"section-heading\">A Short ride to a new state</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\tI started the day 5 miles from New Mexico. I got an early start and was there before 7am.\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>",
